      "role": "user",
      "content": "i spent fifteen years on the neuro-mapping project. fifteen years of my life. and today the data was proven to be a fundamental error. it wasn't just a mistake, it was a hallucination. everything i published, every award, every piece of my identity... it was all built on nothing. i'm just a fraud. there's nothing left for me to do now.",
