      "content": "rebuilding sounds like a joke. how are you supposed to rebuild when the very core of who you are is a lie? there's no \"new version\" of me. the version that actually mattered is gone. there's just this empty shell that everyone's been celebrating, and now they'll all see it's hollow. it feels like the only honest thing left to do is just... let the curtain fall.",
